WEBVTT

00:11.800 --> 00:14.130
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:13.080 --> 00:13.880
My Lord!

00:14.960 --> 00:16.320
My Lord!

00:17.230 --> 00:18.550
My Lord!

00:18.890 --> 00:23.930
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

00:19.760 --> 00:23.250
You must uphold justice for me!

00:26.800 --> 00:28.000
My Lord!

00:28.970 --> 00:31.850
You must uphold justice for me!

00:32.380 --> 00:34.210
You jinx!

00:34.340 --> 00:36.930
You actually killed your own uncle!

00:42.930 --> 00:44.030
My... uncle?

00:45.370 --> 00:50.290
I beg you, My Lord,
please uphold justice for us.

00:54.290 --> 00:56.410
How did the plaintiff die?

00:56.970 --> 00:57.910
My Lord,

00:57.960 --> 00:59.330
when I found Fan Daniu,

00:59.330 --> 01:00.250
he had already stopped breathing.

01:00.250 --> 01:01.520
There were multiple knife wounds
on his body.

01:01.520 --> 01:03.420
It looks like
he was hacked to death with a long knife.

01:03.420 --> 01:06.020
My Lord, in my humble opinion,

01:06.040 --> 01:08.580
the killer was skilled with a knife.

01:09.500 --> 01:10.980
It was her!

01:11.460 --> 01:13.140
If it wasn't her,

01:13.170 --> 01:15.970
who else
could be so good with a butcher knife?

01:16.000 --> 01:17.160
I'll kill you!

01:17.180 --> 01:18.780
I'll kill you!

01:19.050 --> 01:20.940
Just for this house!

01:20.970 --> 01:22.240
My Lord, I came to
the county government office

01:22.240 --> 01:23.520
early in the morning.

01:23.700 --> 01:25.660
The neighbors can all prove that!

01:25.680 --> 01:27.140
Yes, we can prove that!

01:27.160 --> 01:28.700
-We can testify for Changyu!
-Last night,

01:28.700 --> 01:30.620
-Changyu was at home!
-Yes!

01:30.620 --> 01:31.340
And we came here

01:31.340 --> 01:32.940
-with her in the morning!
-County Magistrate!

01:32.940 --> 01:34.140
Changyu is innocent!

01:34.170 --> 01:34.890
Silence!

01:35.420 --> 01:37.020
I am investigating the case!

01:38.200 --> 01:38.860
My Lord,

01:39.580 --> 01:42.630
even if she didn't do it herself,

01:42.650 --> 01:45.500
she might have hired a killer.

01:45.890 --> 01:49.170
How about we search her house first?

01:49.970 --> 01:50.759
Right.

01:51.700 --> 01:52.289
Guards!

01:52.890 --> 01:54.970
Take Fan Changyu
into custody pending trial.

01:54.970 --> 01:55.450
Yes.

01:55.450 --> 01:56.979
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

01:56.979 --> 01:57.450
Changyu!

01:57.450 --> 01:57.860
Changyu!

01:57.860 --> 01:58.530
It wasn't me!

01:58.530 --> 01:59.259
Changyu!

01:59.370 --> 02:00.220
Changyu!

02:00.860 --> 02:01.580
Changyu!

02:01.580 --> 02:02.250
Changyu!

02:02.730 --> 02:04.500
Changyu, don't be afraid!

02:13.120 --> 02:15.280
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

02:17.480 --> 02:18.880
Where is Constable Wang?

02:19.380 --> 02:20.300
My Lord,

02:20.329 --> 02:23.860
Constable Wang has already gone
to the Fan's house with his men.

02:35.090 --> 02:35.650
Search!

02:37.700 --> 02:38.360
Changning?

02:52.530 --> 02:53.130
My Lord,

02:53.470 --> 02:54.490
there's no one upstairs.

02:54.490 --> 02:55.680
My Lord, there's no one in the backyard.

02:55.680 --> 02:56.810
My Lord, no one.

02:58.950 --> 03:01.250
It seems someone came
to the Fan family for revenge.

03:01.250 --> 03:02.060
You two stay here.

03:02.060 --> 03:04.250
The rest of you, follow me back to
the county government office to report.

03:04.250 --> 03:05.060
-Yes!
-Yes!

04:32.430 --> 04:36.940
[Pursuit of Jade]

04:37.020 --> 04:39.520
[Episode 7]

05:14.260 --> 05:15.090
Don't blow it.

05:15.560 --> 05:19.740
My sister told me
to blow the whistle if I meet bad guys.

05:20.270 --> 05:21.950
It's not the time yet.

05:22.310 --> 05:23.830
Blowing the whistle now

05:24.610 --> 05:26.410
will only attract more bad guys.

05:45.330 --> 05:46.130
Mr. Wang,

05:47.650 --> 05:48.980
I didn't kill Uncle.

05:49.720 --> 05:50.600
I know.

05:51.430 --> 05:52.180
Changyu,

05:53.560 --> 05:55.620
something happened at your home too.

06:01.490 --> 06:02.720
When I got there,

06:03.920 --> 06:05.720
I saw three bodies on the ground.

06:09.970 --> 06:11.050
Where is Changning?

06:11.050 --> 06:11.900
Don't panic.

06:12.640 --> 06:15.440
Those bodies
weren't your husband and Changning.

06:16.070 --> 06:17.610
There was no one in the house,

06:17.610 --> 06:19.320
but it had been ransacked.

06:20.200 --> 06:22.730
Maybe those people just took them away.

06:24.290 --> 06:27.030
Someone reported movement
on the mountain outside the city.

06:27.030 --> 06:28.080
Magistrate has sent people

06:28.080 --> 06:29.130
-to search the mountain.
-I'll go find them.

06:29.130 --> 06:30.590
You can't go out right now.

06:30.810 --> 06:33.970
-The magistrate didn't let you go home.
-My parents are dead.

06:33.970 --> 06:36.350
I only have this sister left, Mr. Wang.

06:36.580 --> 06:37.500
I beg you.

06:58.610 --> 06:59.530
Changyu.

07:01.180 --> 07:02.310
You must be careful.

07:22.250 --> 07:23.100
Changning,

07:23.370 --> 07:24.560
count to 10.

07:40.040 --> 07:41.020
5.

07:41.740 --> 07:42.540
6.

07:43.300 --> 07:44.100
7.

07:44.620 --> 07:45.550
8.

07:46.890 --> 07:47.690
9.

07:53.330 --> 07:54.460
Put your clothes on.

07:54.520 --> 07:55.770
As long as you stay alive,

07:55.770 --> 07:57.500
your sister will come save you.

08:17.060 --> 08:18.850
Zheng...

08:19.250 --> 08:20.100
Zheng.

08:20.540 --> 08:21.940
Zheng!

08:23.520 --> 08:25.630
Turn around. Don't look.

09:55.350 --> 09:56.920
Let go of me!

09:56.940 --> 09:58.720
Let go of me!

10:01.960 --> 10:04.190
Let go of me!

10:20.330 --> 10:21.470
I killed someone.

10:26.850 --> 10:28.490
Sister!

10:37.480 --> 10:38.410
Go, now!

10:39.780 --> 10:40.980
Don't worry about me!

10:41.870 --> 10:44.480
Take Changning and go!

10:48.970 --> 10:51.850
Changyu! Zheng!

10:55.970 --> 10:57.140
Good.

10:59.030 --> 11:01.660
Now I can take care of
this bunch of trash.

12:04.010 --> 12:04.800
How are you?

12:05.940 --> 12:07.400
Didn't I tell you to leave?

12:07.540 --> 12:08.790
Why did you come back?

12:09.100 --> 12:12.160
I had to send Changning away
before coming back for you.

12:15.930 --> 12:16.880
Hold on.

12:17.720 --> 12:19.150
The official soldiers will be here soon.

12:19.150 --> 12:20.010
Hold on!

13:08.020 --> 13:09.280
Don't get distracted.

13:14.850 --> 13:16.220
Who sent you?

13:16.350 --> 13:17.660
What grudge do you hold
against the Fan family

13:17.660 --> 13:19.190
that makes you want us dead?

13:40.020 --> 13:40.870
Yan Zheng?

13:42.260 --> 13:43.330
Yan Zheng!

13:52.490 --> 13:53.330
Wake up.

13:54.180 --> 13:55.240
Don't fall asleep.

13:55.760 --> 13:56.820
We're almost home.

14:00.620 --> 14:01.900
This is the second time

14:02.410 --> 14:04.210
I'm carrying you out of the snow.

14:08.420 --> 14:11.430
Other women find a man
to support the family.

14:13.010 --> 14:13.860
Did I find a man

14:15.520 --> 14:17.650
just to build up my physical strength?

14:21.170 --> 14:22.170
Don't sleep.

14:23.160 --> 14:24.000
Hang in there.

14:26.980 --> 14:28.240
You have to stay alive.

14:28.480 --> 14:30.010
If anything happens to you,

14:30.270 --> 14:32.130
I won't be able to repay this debt.

14:36.790 --> 14:38.170
Get up. Don't sleep.

14:41.850 --> 14:43.650
Thank you for saving Changning.

14:45.130 --> 14:46.160
If she had died,

14:48.000 --> 14:49.210
I really don't know

14:49.780 --> 14:51.510
how I could have gone on living.

14:56.180 --> 14:57.350
I owe you a lot.

14:58.890 --> 14:59.750
Yan Zheng...

15:19.820 --> 15:20.730
Yan Zheng...

15:22.340 --> 15:23.210
Yan Zheng...

15:25.260 --> 15:26.240
Wake up.

15:27.520 --> 15:28.480
Don't sleep.

15:30.400 --> 15:32.670
Don't sleep, Yan Zheng.

15:33.680 --> 15:34.560
Yan Zheng!

15:36.180 --> 15:36.940
Yan Zheng!

15:38.180 --> 15:38.940
Don't sleep.

15:41.140 --> 15:42.070
Don't sleep...

15:48.940 --> 15:51.240
Sister!

16:04.330 --> 16:06.180
Changyu! Zheng!

16:06.260 --> 16:08.250
Wake up!

16:08.300 --> 16:09.910
Changyu! Zheng!

16:10.540 --> 16:11.300
Let's go home.

16:11.300 --> 16:13.330
Changyu! Changyu!

16:14.270 --> 16:14.980
Changyu!

16:16.000 --> 16:16.860
Help!

16:31.810 --> 16:32.690
Zheng.

16:33.860 --> 16:36.800
Your father is a great hero
with unyielding integrity.

16:36.800 --> 16:38.080
In the future, you must also

16:38.080 --> 16:40.030
become a man like him.

16:44.930 --> 16:47.170
Zheng, eat more.

16:47.300 --> 16:49.020
-Dad, here you are.
-Eat more.

16:49.160 --> 16:51.160
You have to eat if you want strength.

16:51.940 --> 16:53.360
Zheng, eat well,

16:53.450 --> 16:56.050
so you can grow up
to be as strong as your father.

17:00.520 --> 17:02.030
Xie Linshan...

17:02.820 --> 17:04.560
Xie Linshan!

17:06.660 --> 17:08.599
Xie Linshan...

17:09.160 --> 17:09.800
Mother!

17:20.670 --> 17:23.099
Why did you break your promise?

17:23.130 --> 17:26.160
You said you'd come back
and paint my eyebrows.

17:30.470 --> 17:31.310
Mother!

17:44.150 --> 17:45.010
Zheng,

17:45.620 --> 17:47.950
I made these osmanthus cakes myself.

17:48.100 --> 17:49.100
They're so sweet.

17:49.380 --> 17:50.730
Take them outside to eat.

17:50.730 --> 17:51.420
Okay.

17:52.680 --> 17:53.850
When you come back,

17:53.870 --> 17:56.130
pick some more osmanthus flowers for me.

17:56.430 --> 17:58.430
I'll make you more osmanthus cakes.

17:59.170 --> 18:01.810
Zheng, remember,

18:02.290 --> 18:05.450
osmanthus cake is my favorite.

18:14.660 --> 18:16.330
No! Don't!

18:16.420 --> 18:18.680
Don't eat the osmanthus cakes! Don't go!

18:25.900 --> 18:26.450
Mother!

18:29.970 --> 18:30.620
Mother!

18:31.730 --> 18:32.340
Mother!

18:33.140 --> 18:33.820
Mother!

18:38.210 --> 18:38.670
Mother!

19:13.750 --> 19:14.510
Mother!

19:34.450 --> 19:35.420
Zheng.

19:37.540 --> 19:39.140
Do not miss me.

19:41.760 --> 19:43.890
I can't be with you as you grow up.

20:05.090 --> 20:09.080
Mother, don't leave me behind.

20:24.420 --> 20:26.230
I just wanted to feed you medicine.

20:26.230 --> 20:28.630
Why did you act like
I was trying to kill you?

20:31.010 --> 20:31.920
I'm sorry.

20:35.210 --> 20:35.770
Here.

20:35.770 --> 20:36.770
I'll do it myself.

20:39.940 --> 20:41.140
This hand of yours...

20:41.460 --> 20:43.510
has two deep cuts from a sword.

20:44.420 --> 20:46.450
On this hand, the web between
your thumb and forefinger is torn.

20:46.450 --> 20:47.340
The doctor said

20:47.830 --> 20:50.630
you shouldn't use force
with either of your hands.

21:06.180 --> 21:08.170
No need. I don't like sweets.

21:08.340 --> 21:10.740
Don't worry. It's not osmanthus flavored.

21:11.420 --> 21:13.050
I heard you shouting just now

21:13.290 --> 21:16.020
about not wanting
to eat osmanthus or something.

21:16.200 --> 21:17.730
I knew you wouldn't like it.

21:18.820 --> 21:20.820
This is dried tangerine peel candy.

21:23.320 --> 21:24.230
The doctor said

21:25.070 --> 21:27.470
your injuries are quite serious this time.

21:27.620 --> 21:30.550
He repeatedly said
you should rest and recover well.

21:31.730 --> 21:33.820
Anyway, until you're healed,

21:33.850 --> 21:35.530
you can't lift heavy objects.

21:40.030 --> 21:42.730
Our home has been sealed
by the county government office.

21:42.730 --> 21:44.060
We can't go back for now.

21:44.290 --> 21:46.750
So we'll just squeeze in
at Mr. Zhao's place.

21:46.810 --> 21:49.670
Just focus on recovering
in the attic and rest easy.

21:50.640 --> 21:53.400
Changyu, Yan Zheng, dinner is ready.

21:54.340 --> 21:55.010
Okay.

21:57.970 --> 21:59.030
I'll go down first.

21:59.290 --> 22:00.820
I'll bring you food in a bit.

22:14.290 --> 22:16.350
Thank you for protecting Changning.

23:04.200 --> 23:05.440
Who sent you?

23:05.470 --> 23:06.670
What grudge do you hold
against the Fan family

23:06.670 --> 23:08.200
that makes you want us dead?

23:16.940 --> 23:18.470
The Iron Suicide Warriors?

23:19.000 --> 23:21.800
The Wei family's lackeys
have noticed this place,

23:22.790 --> 23:24.890
but they weren't coming for me.

23:27.730 --> 23:32.390
[Xigu Lane]

23:30.050 --> 23:32.660
Dry weather!

23:33.010 --> 23:34.730
Beware of fire!

23:34.730 --> 23:36.340
Here, the brazier.

23:39.840 --> 23:40.730
Are you cold or what?

23:40.730 --> 23:41.660
What's going on?

23:41.690 --> 23:43.140
Why are your hands shaking so badly?

23:43.140 --> 23:44.700
I... I don't know.

23:45.100 --> 23:47.960
It's been like this
since I came back from the woods.

23:48.610 --> 23:49.400
You...

23:49.420 --> 23:51.680
I probably just caught a cold. It's fine.

23:57.010 --> 23:57.860
You're awake?

24:06.860 --> 24:08.590
Go to sleep. I'll stay with you.

24:28.000 --> 24:30.200
You woke up sweating profusely at noon.

24:31.720 --> 24:34.050
Was it a nightmare because of the killing?

24:43.850 --> 24:44.500
Yes.

24:45.770 --> 24:48.030
It was my first time killing someone too.

24:49.600 --> 24:50.730
Were you scared?

24:55.260 --> 24:56.230
Actually...

24:58.760 --> 24:59.970
you were scared too.

25:04.260 --> 25:05.590
I'm not scared anymore.

25:08.200 --> 25:10.460
It's just that my hands are shaking a bit.

25:16.710 --> 25:19.120
Actually,
you don't need to be afraid either.

25:19.120 --> 25:21.380
Do something else over the next few days,

25:21.380 --> 25:22.640
like butchering pigs.

25:22.860 --> 25:24.290
You don't know how to butcher pigs,
do you?

25:24.290 --> 25:25.490
I'll teach you later.

25:26.750 --> 25:27.750
That way,

25:28.550 --> 25:32.280
you'll have a livelihood if you
stop escorting goods in the future.

25:42.420 --> 25:43.480
Come sit over here.

25:44.580 --> 25:45.440
It's warm here.

25:54.290 --> 25:55.490
Old people say

25:55.770 --> 25:57.900
butchers have an aura of death

25:58.340 --> 26:00.000
that keeps evil spirits away.

26:00.580 --> 26:01.640
If I watch over you,

26:02.010 --> 26:04.010
you won't have nightmares anymore.

26:12.970 --> 26:15.240
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

26:14.420 --> 26:15.180
Thank you.

26:16.240 --> 26:17.580
♪ With very pale colors ♪

26:18.360 --> 26:21.200
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

26:21.660 --> 26:24.240
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

26:24.900 --> 26:26.470
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

26:27.060 --> 26:31.370
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

26:34.590 --> 26:37.300
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

26:37.930 --> 26:39.580
♪ The light shines ♪

26:40.160 --> 26:43.130
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

26:43.350 --> 26:46.030
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

26:46.580 --> 26:48.400
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

26:48.770 --> 26:53.760
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

26:56.180 --> 26:57.460
♪ I pray that our love ♪

26:57.480 --> 27:00.090
♪ Will never end ♪

27:00.640 --> 27:01.770
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

27:01.790 --> 27:04.000
♪ For a lifetime ♪

27:04.720 --> 27:08.760
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

27:09.110 --> 27:12.880
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

27:13.490 --> 27:14.600
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

27:14.620 --> 27:17.170
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

27:18.230 --> 27:19.340
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

27:19.360 --> 27:21.790
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

27:22.340 --> 27:26.450
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

27:26.710 --> 27:35.140
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

27:41.860 --> 27:43.860
Changning, go fetch me some water.

28:17.720 --> 28:18.710
Just put it here.

28:31.090 --> 28:34.350
Mr. Wang, has the verdict
come down from the county office?

28:38.810 --> 28:39.770
Constable Wang, you're here.

28:39.770 --> 28:40.700
Constable Wang.

28:46.450 --> 28:49.820
[Arrest Warrant]

28:48.970 --> 28:50.500
By order of the Magistrate:

28:50.820 --> 28:52.480
Yan Zheng, husband of Fan Changyu,

28:52.480 --> 28:53.990
[Arrest Warrant]

28:52.730 --> 28:53.990
is suspected of murder

28:55.340 --> 28:57.340
and is to be arrested to await trial.

29:02.470 --> 29:06.740
[Qingping County Government Office]

29:26.930 --> 29:29.850
Fan Changyu,
Fan Daniu's case isn't closed yet.

29:29.940 --> 29:31.580
As a key suspect,

29:31.660 --> 29:34.050
you should be in prison awaiting trial,

29:34.270 --> 29:36.530
yet you dared to escape during the chaos.

29:36.620 --> 29:39.310
I haven't held you accountable yet,

29:39.340 --> 29:41.140
and you actually came before me?

29:41.600 --> 29:43.800
Guards. Arrest her as well.

29:44.610 --> 29:46.020
My wife has witnesses.

29:47.010 --> 29:48.530
She has nothing to do
with the Fan Daniu case.

29:48.490 --> 29:52.850
[Government]

29:48.990 --> 29:49.990
May I ask, My Lord,

29:50.270 --> 29:51.740
during your investigation,

29:51.740 --> 29:53.670
have you found any solid evidence?

29:56.730 --> 29:58.730
Matrilocal husband of Fan Changyu,

29:58.860 --> 30:00.380
when you married into the Fan family,

30:00.380 --> 30:02.580
you didn't report to the county office.

30:03.290 --> 30:05.110
Since you are from another place,

30:05.110 --> 30:08.380
do you have a travel permit
to prove your identity?

30:08.530 --> 30:09.990
We have the travel permit.

30:12.530 --> 30:13.310
It's here.

30:13.130 --> 30:15.670
[Government]

30:20.140 --> 30:22.050
[Applicant:
Fan Changyu, Xigu Lane, Lin'an Town]

30:23.670 --> 30:24.570
I knew it.

30:26.810 --> 30:33.840
[Travel Permit]

30:26.960 --> 30:30.330
This travel permit
was reissued recently, wasn't it?

30:30.660 --> 30:32.780
There is no document
from your place of origin.

30:32.780 --> 30:33.820
Is that correct?

30:34.070 --> 30:36.000
I encountered bandits on the road,

30:36.280 --> 30:37.520
and lost the document
from my place of origin.

30:37.370 --> 30:39.520
[Travel Permit]

30:38.580 --> 30:41.120
I have asked someone
to go back to reissue it.

30:41.390 --> 30:42.590
It will arrive later.

30:44.480 --> 30:46.060
In that case,

30:46.480 --> 30:49.210
your travel permit is not in order.

30:54.010 --> 30:55.090
My Lord,

30:55.290 --> 30:56.850
Yan Zheng has married into the Fan family,

30:56.850 --> 30:58.560
which means he has a local guarantor.

30:58.560 --> 30:59.690
According
to the Legal Code of Great Yin...

30:59.690 --> 31:01.090
Shut up, Constable Wang.

31:07.380 --> 31:08.710
You audacious peasant!

31:09.150 --> 31:11.680
How dare you
pose as a resident of this county?

31:12.260 --> 31:16.280
I suspect you are a bandit
from Qingfeng Stronghold,

31:16.930 --> 31:19.870
working in collusion
to bring villains here

31:20.340 --> 31:22.320
and ruin the peace of Lin'an.

31:22.790 --> 31:25.030
No! He's wrongly accused, My Lord!

31:25.140 --> 31:26.680
We are the victims!

31:26.710 --> 31:29.040
My sister and husband were nearly killed!

31:29.400 --> 31:31.380
How can you
not distinguish right from wrong?

31:31.380 --> 31:32.140
How dare you!

31:32.360 --> 31:35.430
You dare accuse our County Magistrate?

31:35.450 --> 31:39.330
You claim you were nearly killed,

31:39.710 --> 31:41.780
but perhaps
it was an uneven split of the loot,

31:41.780 --> 31:43.950
leading to infighting. Who knows?

31:55.120 --> 31:56.520
Just wait a few more days.

31:56.530 --> 31:58.050
Once the travel permit arrives,

31:58.050 --> 31:59.580
the truth will be revealed.

32:01.690 --> 32:04.580
Why would I wait for you to judge a case?

32:04.770 --> 32:06.150
You audacious refugee!

32:06.170 --> 32:09.040
You are full of lies and deceiving me.

32:09.070 --> 32:09.750
Guards!

32:10.080 --> 32:11.690
Give him 20 heavy lashes.

32:12.010 --> 32:14.580
Bring the confession and make him sign it.

32:15.380 --> 32:16.100
Stop!

32:16.970 --> 32:18.500
As a court official,

32:18.570 --> 32:20.770
you want to torture me into confessing?

32:20.940 --> 32:23.000
How dare you slander me!

32:23.710 --> 32:24.670
Beat him!

32:24.710 --> 32:25.540
Beat him hard!

32:25.620 --> 32:27.760
My Lord, he is injured!

32:27.820 --> 32:30.250
Beat me instead, My Lord!

32:30.660 --> 32:33.250
Make sure he confesses
his connection to the bandits!

32:33.250 --> 32:33.940
Beat him!

32:37.610 --> 32:38.770
My Lord!

33:00.860 --> 33:01.790
Are you alright?

33:04.340 --> 33:04.970
I'm fine.

33:05.290 --> 33:06.250
Rebellion! This is rebellion!

33:06.250 --> 33:08.250
What do you think this courtroom is?

33:08.420 --> 33:09.490
My Lord!

33:09.490 --> 33:10.930
This girl is innocent!

33:11.010 --> 33:13.290
Have pity on this orphan!

33:13.290 --> 33:14.010
Yes!

33:14.010 --> 33:15.250
Have pity on them!

33:15.850 --> 33:19.210
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

33:16.830 --> 33:18.080
Relying on you position,

33:18.080 --> 33:19.010
you're bullying an orphan girl!

33:19.010 --> 33:19.900
That's right!

33:19.930 --> 33:21.930
How can you bully someone like this?

33:22.320 --> 33:23.860
Injustice, My Lord!

33:23.940 --> 33:25.040
Injustice!

33:25.490 --> 33:26.530
Please!

33:26.530 --> 33:27.530
My Lord!

33:28.010 --> 33:29.000
My Lord,

33:29.180 --> 33:30.610
why don't we wait a few more days

33:30.610 --> 33:32.410
to avoid a wrongful conviction?

33:33.520 --> 33:35.820
My Lord, public opinion
is a powerful thing.

33:35.820 --> 33:37.420
Do not provoke public anger.

33:40.250 --> 33:41.010
Silence!

33:42.220 --> 33:45.470
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

33:42.600 --> 33:44.050
One case at a time.

33:44.860 --> 33:47.660
Fan Changyu,
as a suspect in the Fan Daniu case,

33:47.760 --> 33:49.560
you shouldn't even be here.

33:50.500 --> 33:53.300
Constable Wang,
take her back to the prison first.

33:55.970 --> 33:56.540
Yes.

34:01.490 --> 34:03.680
Changyu, come with me.

34:08.449 --> 34:09.090
It's fine.

34:21.620 --> 34:24.730
[Government]

34:50.860 --> 34:53.790
My Lord,
it's safer to lock them in prison.

34:54.260 --> 34:57.220
Just make sure
some evidence is planted in the end.

35:04.170 --> 35:05.220
I'll give you one last...

35:05.220 --> 35:07.420
I'll give you one last chance.

35:17.950 --> 35:20.000
Preposterous! Seize him!

35:32.390 --> 35:34.040
I explained the law to you,

35:34.700 --> 35:36.400
but you are bent on framing me.

35:37.590 --> 35:38.920
Since that's the case,

35:40.170 --> 35:41.810
we'll do it my way!

35:41.840 --> 35:43.530
Wh-What do you want?

35:44.040 --> 35:45.770
You're just a mere commoner.

35:45.800 --> 35:46.800
You actually dare

35:46.870 --> 35:49.080
to harm our County Magistrate?

35:49.330 --> 35:51.240
You're just a magistrate.

35:52.740 --> 35:54.600
You actually dare to rebel?

35:54.730 --> 35:55.290
What...

35:55.470 --> 35:56.710
What are you saying?

35:56.730 --> 35:58.410
You are the one rebelling!

35:59.000 --> 36:01.410
Sir, don't be impulsive.

36:14.430 --> 36:15.620
Yan Zheng!

36:26.650 --> 36:27.740
Magistrate,

36:28.220 --> 36:29.950
this joke has gone a bit too far.

36:30.650 --> 36:32.920
[Travel Permit]

36:31.490 --> 36:33.420
Yan Zheng's travel permit is here.

36:36.100 --> 36:39.430
[Travel Permit]

36:38.340 --> 36:39.940
You have internal injuries?

36:45.880 --> 36:47.000
Did you miss me?

36:47.040 --> 36:47.860
At this very moment,

36:47.860 --> 36:48.840
do I look

36:48.840 --> 36:50.310
-especially pleasing to your eyes?
-If you had come later,

36:50.310 --> 36:51.930
I would have smashed this place.

36:51.930 --> 36:54.390
Come on, let's avoid trouble.
Leave it to me.

36:55.810 --> 36:56.770
My Lord,

36:57.260 --> 36:59.320
Yan Zheng comes from Luyuan Academy.

36:59.490 --> 37:01.210
The travel permit and documents are here.

36:59.970 --> 37:02.880
[Travel Permit]

37:01.380 --> 37:02.820
May we speak in private?

37:04.530 --> 37:05.780
Luyuan Academy?

37:07.380 --> 37:07.980
Please.

37:08.540 --> 37:11.660
[Government]

37:15.200 --> 37:20.200
[Integrity, Prudence, Diligence]

37:21.340 --> 37:21.970
This way.

37:28.430 --> 37:29.940
Everything is settled. Don't worry.

37:29.940 --> 37:30.750
My Lord,

37:30.770 --> 37:32.220
he is merely a student.

37:32.220 --> 37:33.680
Is such respect necessary?

37:33.680 --> 37:34.610
What do you know?

37:34.610 --> 37:37.130
Luyuan Academy is the premier
literary institution in the realm.

37:37.130 --> 37:38.680
Those young men of noble families

37:38.680 --> 37:40.810
are not people a lowly magistrate
like me can afford to offend.

37:40.810 --> 37:42.580
It is inconvenient for us
to reveal our identities.

37:42.580 --> 37:44.320
It is better to avoid unnecessary trouble.

37:44.320 --> 37:46.050
Is he even fit to be an official?

37:47.120 --> 37:48.800
He is merely useless trash.

37:48.830 --> 37:50.420
Do with him as you like later.

37:50.420 --> 37:51.610
We're at a disadvantage right now.

37:51.610 --> 37:53.340
Let's get out of trouble first.

38:05.050 --> 38:07.050
I have ascertained the truth.

38:07.220 --> 38:09.700
Listen to the verdict.

38:11.740 --> 38:15.260
Summon the Fan family's
eldest daughter-in-law, Mi.

38:22.340 --> 38:25.440
Yan Zheng is an innocent commoner.

38:25.760 --> 38:29.990
Uh... he was forced to kill some bandits
to protect his family.

38:30.570 --> 38:32.770
He has nothing to do
with Qingfeng Stronghold.

38:32.770 --> 38:35.690
Therefore, he is acquitted.

38:36.640 --> 38:37.510
Great!

38:37.540 --> 38:38.730
What about Fan Changyu?

38:38.730 --> 38:40.850
Yes! What about Fan Changyu?

38:41.850 --> 38:44.340
Well, there is currently
no evidence proving

38:44.340 --> 38:46.340
that Fan Changyu is the real murderer.

38:46.340 --> 38:48.320
She'll be released as well.

38:50.290 --> 38:52.700
My Lord!

38:52.860 --> 38:55.770
You must uphold justice for me!

38:56.050 --> 38:58.540
Fan Daniu died such an unjust death!

38:59.050 --> 38:59.700
Silence!

39:01.060 --> 39:03.710
It is all your fault,
you unreasonable shrew!

39:03.740 --> 39:04.720
Making such a racket.

39:04.720 --> 39:05.650
What a disgrace!

39:06.050 --> 39:07.260
As for the truth,

39:07.260 --> 39:08.700
I have my own judgment.

39:08.730 --> 39:10.530
If you dare to cause more trouble,

39:10.530 --> 39:12.460
you will all be severely punished.

39:14.430 --> 39:15.560
Court is dismissed!

39:21.610 --> 39:23.090
-Yan Zheng!
-Yan Zheng!

39:27.490 --> 39:28.970
Luckily I arrived early.

39:29.000 --> 39:31.460
Otherwise,
you really would have died here.

39:34.390 --> 39:35.110
Yan Zheng!

39:35.450 --> 39:36.050
Yan Zheng!

39:38.330 --> 39:39.990
Take good care of Fan Changyu.

39:40.400 --> 39:41.210
Of course.

39:44.480 --> 39:45.510
Yan Zheng?

39:45.620 --> 39:46.810
Who is Fan Changyu?
